---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Technik Informatyk - ZSEiU Łaziska Górne" description="Technik informatyk w ZSEiU Łaziska Górne – programowanie, sieci, bazy danych, cyberbezpieczeństwo. Kształcenie praktyczne w nowoczesnych pracowniach.">

  <article class="w-full max-w-5xl mx-auto min-w-0">

    <!-- HERO -->
    <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-900 via-navy-950 to-slate-900 dark:from-navy-950 dark:via-navy-900 dark:to-navy-950 border border-slate-700/50 dark:border-navy-700/50 p-5 sm:p-10 mb-10 w-full">
      <div class="cyber-grid absolute inset-0 opacity-20" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="cyber-glow absolute -top-20 -right-20 w-80 h-80 bg-primary-500/10 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="cyber-glow absolute -bottom-20 -left-20 w-80 h-80 bg-blue-500/10 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="relative z-10">
        <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold bg-primary-500/20 text-primary-300 border border-primary-500/30 mb-4">Kierunek 2025/2026</span>
        <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white mb-3 leading-tight break-words">Technik <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-300 via-primary-400 to-blue-400">Informatyk</span></h1>
        <p class="text-base sm:text-xl text-slate-300 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed break-words">Zawód przyszłości w cyfrowym świecie – programowanie, sieci, cyberbezpieczeństwo i nowoczesne technologie.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- STATYSTYKI -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-4 gap-3 sm:gap-4 my-10 w-full">
      <div class="stat-card rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-navy-800/70 border border-slate-200 dark:border-navy-700 p-3 sm:p-5 text-center min-w-0" data-count-to="95">
        <span class="block text-2xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400"><span class="stat-value">0</span>%</span>
        <span class="block mt-1 text-xs sm:text-base text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 leading-snug">zajęć praktycznych</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-navy-800/70 border border-slate-200 dark:border-navy-700 p-3 sm:p-5 text-center min-w-0" data-count-to="100">
        <span class="block text-2xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400"><span class="stat-value">0</span>+</span>
        <span class="block mt-1 text-xs sm:text-base text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 leading-snug">stanowisk laboratoryjnych</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-navy-800/70 border border-slate-200 dark:border-navy-700 p-3 sm:p-5 text-center min-w-0" data-count-to="20">
        <span class="block text-2xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400"><span class="stat-value">0</span></span>
        <span class="block mt-1 text-xs sm:text-base text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 leading-snug">lat doświadczenia w kształceniu IT</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-navy-800/70 border border-slate-200 dark:border-navy-700 p-3 sm:p-5 text-center min-w-0" data-count-to="100">
        <span class="block text-2xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400"><span class="stat-value">0</span>%</span>
        <span class="block mt-1 text-xs sm:text-base text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 leading-snug">zdawalności egzaminów zawodowych</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- TECHNOLOGIE -->
    <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mt-10 mb-6 pl-3 sm:pl-4 border-l-4 border-primary-500 leading-snug break-words">Technologie, których uczymy</h2>

    <p class="text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 mb-6 break-words">
      Nauka odbywa się w oparciu o narzędzia i platformy stosowane w profesjonalnych środowiskach IT.
    </p>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 xs:grid-cols-3 sm:grid-cols-4 lg:grid-cols-7 gap-3 mb-8 w-full">
      <div class="tech-chip rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-navy-800/70 border border-slate-200 dark:border-navy-700 p-3 sm:p-4 text-center min-w-0 hover:border-primary-300 dark:hover:border-primary-700 hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 mx-auto mb-2 rounded-lg bg-slate-100 dark:bg-navy-700 flex items-center justify-center text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 shrink-0">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="w-6 h-6"><path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-1 17.93c-3.95-.49-7-3.85-7-7.93 0-.62.08-1.21.21-1.79L9 15v1c0 1.1.9 2 2 2v1.93zm6.9-2.54c-.26-.81-1-1.39-1.9-1.39h-1v-3c0-.55-.45-1-1-1H8v-2h2c.55 0 1-.45 1-1V7h2c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2v-.41c2.93 1.19 5 4.06 5 7.41 0 2.08-.8 3.97-2.1 5.39z"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <span class="block text-xs sm:text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white break-words">Linux</span>
      </div>
      <div class="tech-chip rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-navy-800/70 border border-slate-200 dark:border-navy-700 p-3 sm:p-4 text-center min-w-0 hover:border-primary-300 dark:hover:border-primary-700 hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 mx-auto mb-2 rounded-lg bg-slate-100 dark:bg-navy-700 flex items-center justify-center text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 shrink-0">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="w-6 h-6"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2"></rect><path d="M8 21h8"></path><path d="M12 17v4"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <span class="block text-xs sm:text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white break-words">Windows Server</span>
      </div>
      <div class="tech-chip rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-navy-800/70 border border-slate-200 dark:border-navy-700 p-3 sm:p-4 text-center min-w-0 hover:border-primary-300 dark:hover:border-primary-700 hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 mx-auto mb-2 rounded-lg bg-slate-100 dark:bg-navy-700 flex items-center justify-center text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 shrink-0">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" class="w-6 h-6"><path d="M4 22h16a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V4a2 2 0 0 0-2-2H8a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 1-2 2zm0 0a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-9h4"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <span class="block text-xs sm:text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white break-words">Cisco</span>
      </div>
      <div class="tech-chip rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-navy-800/70 border border-slate-200 dark:border-navy-700 p-3 sm:p-4 text-center min-w-0 hover:border-primary-300 dark:hover:border-primary-700 hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 mx-auto mb-2 rounded-lg bg-slate-100 dark:bg-navy-700 flex items-center justify-center text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 shrink-0">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" class="w-6 h-6"><path d="M20 7l-8 4-8-4"></path><path d="M12 21V11"></path><path d="M4 7v10l8 4 8-4V7"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <span class="block text-xs sm:text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white break-words">Docker</span>
      </div>
      <div class="tech-chip rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-navy-800/70 border border-slate-200 dark:border-navy-700 p-3 sm:p-4 text-center min-w-0 hover:border-primary-300 dark:hover:border-primary-700 hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 mx-auto mb-2 rounded-lg bg-slate-100 dark:bg-navy-700 flex items-center justify-center text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 shrink-0">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="w-6 h-6"><path d="M8 3a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v4a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h2v2h-2a4 4 0 0 1-4-4V5a4 4 0 0 1 4-4h8a4 4 0 0 1 4 4v4a4 4 0 0 1-4 4h-2v-2h2a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2H8z"></path><path d="M9 13h6v2H9z"></path><path d="M11 17h2v4h-2z"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <span class="block text-xs sm:text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white break-words">Python</span>
      </div>
      <div class="tech-chip rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-navy-800/70 border border-slate-200 dark:border-navy-700 p-3 sm:p-4 text-center min-w-0 hover:border-primary-300 dark:hover:border-primary-700 hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 mx-auto mb-2 rounded-lg bg-slate-100 dark:bg-navy-700 flex items-center justify-center text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 shrink-0">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" class="w-6 h-6"><polyline points="16 18 22 12 16 6"></polyline><polyline points="8 6 2 12 8 18"></polyline></svg>
        </div>
        <span class="block text-xs sm:text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white break-words">JavaScript</span>
      </div>
      <div class="tech-chip rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-navy-800/70 border border-slate-200 dark:border-navy-700 p-3 sm:p-4 text-center min-w-0 hover:border-primary-300 dark:hover:border-primary-700 hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 mx-auto mb-2 rounded-lg bg-slate-100 dark:bg-navy-700 flex items-center justify-center text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 shrink-0">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" class="w-6 h-6"><ellipse cx="12" cy="5" rx="9" ry="3"></ellipse><path d="M21 12c0 1.66-4 3-9 3s-9-1.34-9-3"></path><path d="M3 5v14c0 1.66 4 3 9 3s9-1.34 9-3V5"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <span class="block text-xs sm:text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white break-words">SQL</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- CZEGO SIĘ NAUCZYSZ -->
    <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mt-10 mb-6 pl-3 sm:pl-4 border-l-4 border-primary-500 leading-snug break-words">Czego nauczysz się podczas nauki?</h2>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-8 w-full">
      <div class="skill-card rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-navy-800/70 border border-slate-200 dark:border-navy-700 p-4 sm:p-5 hover:shadow-md hover:border-primary-300 dark:hover:border-primary-700 transition-all duration-300 min-w-0">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-primary-100 dark:bg-primary-900/40 flex items-center justify-center text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="w-5 h-5"><polyline points="16 18 22 12 16 6"></polyline><polyline points="8 6 2 12 8 18"></polyline></svg></span>
          <div class="min-w-0 flex-1">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white break-words">Programowanie i tworzenie aplikacji</h3>
            <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1 text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 list-disc list-inside">
              <li>aplikacje desktopowe, internetowe i mobilne</li>
              <li>nowoczesne języki programowania (Python, JavaScript, C++)</li>
              <li>projektowanie i testowanie oprogramowania</li>
              <li>systemy kontroli wersji (Git)</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="skill-card rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-navy-800/70 border border-slate-200 dark:border-navy-700 p-4 sm:p-5 hover:shadow-md hover:border-primary-300 dark:hover:border-primary-700 transition-all duration-300 min-w-0">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-primary-100 dark:bg-primary-900/40 flex items-center justify-center text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="w-5 h-5"><path d="M4 22h16a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V4a2 2 0 0 0-2-2H8a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 1-2 2zm0 0a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-9h4"></path></svg></span>
          <div class="min-w-0 flex-1">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white break-words">Sieci komputerowe</h3>
            <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1 text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 list-disc list-inside">
              <li>projektowanie i budowa sieci lokalnych (Cisco)</li>
              <li>konfiguracja urządzeń sieciowych</li>
              <li>administrowanie usługami sieciowymi</li>
              <li>diagnozowanie i usuwanie usterek</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="skill-card rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-navy-800/70 border border-slate-200 dark:border-navy-700 p-4 sm:p-5 hover:shadow-md hover:border-primary-300 dark:hover:border-primary-700 transition-all duration-300 min-w-0">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-primary-100 dark:bg-primary-900/40 flex items-center justify-center text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="w-5 h-5"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2"></rect><path d="M8 21h8"></path><path d="M12 17v4"></path></svg></span>
          <div class="min-w-0 flex-1">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white break-words">Systemy operacyjne</h3>
            <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1 text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 list-disc list-inside">
              <li>instalacja i konfiguracja Windows Server oraz Linux</li>
              <li>zarządzanie użytkownikami i zasobami</li>
              <li>automatyzacja zadań administracyjnych</li>
              <li>utrzymanie bezpieczeństwa systemów</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="skill-card rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-navy-800/70 border border-slate-200 dark:border-navy-700 p-4 sm:p-5 hover:shadow-md hover:border-primary-300 dark:hover:border-primary-700 transition-all duration-300 min-w-0">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-primary-100 dark:bg-primary-900/40 flex items-center justify-center text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="w-5 h-5"><ellipse cx="12" cy="5" rx="9" ry="3"></ellipse><path d="M21 12c0 1.66-4 3-9 3s-9-1.34-9-3"></path><path d="M3 5v14c0 1.66 4 3 9 3s9-1.34 9-3V5"></path></svg></span>
          <div class="min-w-0 flex-1">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white break-words">Bazy danych</h3>
            <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1 text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 list-disc list-inside">
              <li>projektowanie struktur baz danych (SQL, MySQL)</li>
              <li>tworzenie zapytań SQL</li>
              <li>administrowanie bazami danych</li>
              <li>integracja baz danych z aplikacjami</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="skill-card rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-navy-800/70 border border-slate-200 dark:border-navy-700 p-4 sm:p-5 hover:shadow-md hover:border-primary-300 dark:hover:border-primary-700 transition-all duration-300 min-w-0">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-primary-100 dark:bg-primary-900/40 flex items-center justify-center text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="w-5 h-5"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"></path></svg></span>
          <div class="min-w-0 flex-1">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white break-words">Cyberbezpieczeństwo</h3>
            <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1 text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 list-disc list-inside">
              <li>ochrona danych i systemów informatycznych</li>
              <li>wykrywanie zagrożeń i reagowanie na incydenty</li>
              <li>dobre praktyki bezpieczeństwa</li>
              <li>zabezpieczanie infrastruktury sieciowej</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="skill-card rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-navy-800/70 border border-slate-200 dark:border-navy-700 p-4 sm:p-5 hover:shadow-md hover:border-primary-300 dark:hover:border-primary-700 transition-all duration-300 min-w-0">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-primary-100 dark:bg-primary-900/40 flex items-center justify-center text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="w-5 h-5"><rect x="2" y="2" width="20" height="8" rx="2"></rect><rect x="2" y="14" width="20" height="8" rx="2"></rect><path d="M6 6h.01M6 18h.01"></path></svg></span>
          <div class="min-w-0 flex-1">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white break-words">Sprzęt komputerowy</h3>
            <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1 text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 list-disc list-inside">
              <li>montaż i modernizacja komputerów</li>
              <li>diagnostyka podzespołów</li>
              <li>konfiguracja urządzeń peryferyjnych</li>
              <li>serwisowanie sprzętu komputerowego</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- TIMELINE 5 LAT -->
    <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mt-10 mb-6 pl-3 sm:pl-4 border-l-4 border-primary-500 leading-snug break-words">Jak wygląda nauka w technikum?</h2>

    <p class="text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 mb-6 break-words">
      Nauka w technikum trwa 5 lat. Przez pierwsze trzy lata zdobywasz wiedzę z zakresu sprzętu komputerowego, sieci i administrowania (INF.02), a od trzeciej klasy rozpoczniesz naukę tworzenia stron i aplikacji internetowych oraz baz danych (INF.03).
    </p>

    <div class="relative mb-8 w-full">
      <div class="hidden sm:block absolute left-1/2 top-0 bottom-0 w-0.5 bg-slate-200 dark:bg-navy-700 -translate-x-1/2"></div>
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="relative flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-start gap-4 sm:gap-8">
          <div class="hidden sm:flex sm:w-1/2 justify-end">
            <div class="text-right">
              <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-slate-200 dark:bg-navy-700 text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 font-bold text-sm mb-1">I</span>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Sprzęt komputerowy i podstawy IT</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Montaż PC, systemy operacyjne, diagnostyka</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="hidden sm:flex shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-primary-500 items-center justify-center ring-4 ring-white dark:ring-navy-900 z-10">
            <span class="text-white font-bold text-xs">1</span>
          </div>
          <div class="w-full sm:w-1/2">
            <div class="sm:hidden flex items-center gap-3 mb-1">
              <span class="shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-primary-500 flex items-center justify-center ring-2 ring-white dark:ring-navy-900"><span class="text-white font-bold text-xs">1</span></span>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white min-w-0 flex-1 break-words">Klasa I – Sprzęt komputerowy i podstawy IT</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 sm:hidden">Montaż PC, systemy operacyjne, diagnostyka</p>
            <p class="hidden sm:block text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 mt-1">Poznajesz budowę komputera, uczysz się montować i diagnozować podzespoły. Instalujesz systemy operacyjne i konfigurujesz urządzenia peryferyjne.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="relative flex flex-col sm:flex-row-reverse items-start gap-4 sm:gap-8">
          <div class="hidden sm:flex sm:w-1/2">
            <div>
              <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-slate-200 dark:bg-navy-700 text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 font-bold text-sm mb-1">II</span>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Sieci komputerowe i administrowanie</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Cisco, Windows Server, Linux, konfiguracja sieci</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="hidden sm:flex shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-blue-500 items-center justify-center ring-4 ring-white dark:ring-navy-900 z-10">
            <span class="text-white font-bold text-xs">2</span>
          </div>
